{"type":"message","id":"be11f5aa","parentId":"db942ec1","timestamp":"2026-03-22T01:31:13.806Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我找到了这些元素，但它们没有明显的onclick或data属性。这意味着它们可能是通过Vue或React的事件绑定处理的。\n\n让我尝试另一种方法：直接使用aria快照中的ref来点击这些元素。从之前的快照中，我看到了这些元素的ref。让我重新获取快照，然后尝试点击。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我重新获取完整的页面快照，并尝试点击导航菜单："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ebab3b799ade4cc8b66c270c","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"snapshot","depth":2,"maxChars":80000,"refs":"aria","targetId":"26A65F7EE9C46B98ACD58D0C72FF8AC2"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1860,"output":137,"cacheRead":54080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56077,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774143067314}}
