{"type":"message","id":"835c6113","parentId":"1a2a97c0","timestamp":"2026-03-22T01:31:22.999Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"页面快照结果不完整。让我尝试另一种方式 - 直接通过JavaScript获取导航菜单的结构，然后模拟点击。\n\n由于页面使用了前端框架（可能是Vue），让我尝试直接获取__vue__组件信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f5c83266e9004f0280c34816","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","fn":"\n(function() {\n  var result = [];\n  var vueComponents = [];\n  var allElements = document.querySelectorAll('*');\n  for (var i = 0; i < allElements.length && i < 1000; i++) {\n    var el = allElements[i];\n    if (el.__vue__) {\n      vueComponents.push({tagName: el.tagName, className: el.className, hasVue: true});\n    }\n  }\n  return JSON.stringify({vueComponentsCount: vueComponents.length, sample: vueComponents.slice(0, 5)});\n})()\n","kind":"evaluate","targetId":"26A65F7EE9C46B98ACD58D0C72FF8AC2"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":375,"output":207,"cacheRead":55936,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56518,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774143074209}}
{"type":"message","id":"9d20d73f","parentId":"835c6113","timestamp":"2026-03-22T01:31:23.159Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f5c83266e9004f0280c34816","toolName":"browser","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"ok\": true,\n  \"targetId\": \"26A65F7EE9C46B98ACD58D0C72FF8AC2\",\n  \"url\": \"https://vip.kingdee.com/knowledge/specialDetail/218022218066869248?productLineId=29&lang=zh-CN\",\n  \"result\": \"{\\\"vueComponentsCount\\\":67,\\\"sample\\\":[{\\\"tagName\\\":\\\"DIV\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"hasVue\\\":true},{\\\"tagName\\\":\\\"DIV\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"hasVue\\\":true},{\\\"tagName\\\":\\\"DIV\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"body-default clear-margin-down knowledge-specialDetail-id\\\",\\\"hasVue\\\":true},{\\\"tagName\\\":\\\"HEADER\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"app-header app-header-bg no-scrolled page-header-knowledge-specialDetail-id no-login has-lang-switch\\\",\\\"hasVue\\\":true},{\\\"tagName\\\":\\\"DIV\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"nav-brand-logo\\\",\\\"hasVue\\\":true}]}\"\n}"}],"details":{"ok":true,"targetId":"26A65F7EE9C46B98ACD58D0C72FF8AC2","url":"https://vip.kingdee.com/knowledge/specialDetail/218022218066869248?productLineId=29&lang=zh-CN","result":"{\"vueComponentsCount\":67,\"sample\":[{\"tagName\":\"DIV\",\"className\":\"\",\"hasVue\":true},{\"tagName\":\"DIV\",\"className\":\"\",\"hasVue\":true},{\"tagName\":\"DIV\",\"className\":\"body-default clear-margin-down knowledge-specialDetail-id\",\"hasVue\":true},{\"tagName\":\"HEADER\",\"className\":\"app-header app-header-bg no-scrolled page-header-knowledge-specialDetail-id no-login has-lang-switch\",\"hasVue\":true},{\"tagName\":\"DIV\",\"className\":\"nav-brand-logo\",\"hasVue\":true}]}"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774143083145}}
{"type":"message","id":"2d55d885","parentId":"9d20d73f","timestamp":"2026-03-22T01:31:35.267Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"页面使用了Vue框架。让我尝试找到导航菜单的Vue组件并获取其数据。\n\n不过，让我换一种思路。既然页面需要登录，而且我已经看到了页面结构，我可以尝试：\n\n1. 直接访问每个文档的URL（如果能找到URL模式）\n2. 或者尝试通过JavaScript触发导航菜单的点击事件\n\n让我先尝试找到文档的URL模式。从之前的快照中，我注意到页面URL是 specialDetail/{id}。让我尝试通过JavaScript获取导航菜单中存储的文档ID或URL。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4b4314190f73430c90d9aec7","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","fn":"\n(function() {\n  var result = [];\n  var menuItems = document.querySelectorAll('[class*=\"special-menu\"], [class*=\"menu-item\"], [class*=\"tree-node\"]');\n  for (var i = 0; i < menuItems.length; i++) {\n    var item = menuItems[i];\n    var text = (item.textContent || '').trim().substring(0, 50);\n    var dataId = item.getAttribute('data-id') || item.getAttribute('data-key') || item.id;\n    var vueData = item.__vue__ ? 'hasVue' : 'noVue';\n    result.push({text: text, dataId: dataId, vueData: vueData, className: item.className});\n  }\n  return JSON.stringify(result.slice(0, 20));\n})()\n","kind":"evaluate","targetId":"26A65F7EE9C46B98ACD58D0C72FF8AC2"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":455,"output":320,"cacheRead":56256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57031,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774143083170}}
{"type":"message","id":"a0383435","parentId":"2d55d885","timestamp":"2026-03-22T01:31:35.389Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4b4314190f73430c90d9aec7","toolName":"browser","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"ok\": true,\n  \"targetId\": \"26A65F7EE9C46B98ACD58D0C72FF8AC2\",\n  \"url\": \"https://vip.kingdee.com/knowledge/specialDetail/218022218066869248?productLineId=29&lang=zh-CN\",\n  \"result\": \"[{\\\"text\\\":\\\"签到成长中心联系我们\\\\n            徐少春个人号\\\\n          您可以与徐少春先生交\\\",\\\"dataId\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"vueData\\\":\\\"noVue\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"menu-item\\\"}]\"\n}"}],"details":{"ok":true,"targetId":"26A65F7EE9C46B98ACD58D0C72FF8AC2","url":"https://vip.kingdee.com/knowledge/specialDetail/218022218066869248?productLineId=29&lang=zh-CN","result":"[{\"text\":\"签到成长中心联系我们\\n            徐少春个人号\\n          您可以与徐少春先生交\",\"dataId\":\"\",\"vueData\":\"noVue\",\"className\":\"menu-item\"}]"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774143095384}}
{"type":"message","id":"4b0a667f","parentId":"a0383435","timestamp":"2026-03-22T01:31:47.187Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我尝试更直接的方法：通过JavaScript获取Vue实例的数据，或者通过监听网络请求来获取文档URL。\n\n实际上，让我换一种更直接的方式：使用快照中的ref直接点击导航菜单项。但首先我需要确保导航菜单是展开的。\n\n让我尝试通过JavaScript模拟鼠标点击来展开\"控件使用指南\"菜单。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_49ce125dca0b4a42a1487ca5","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","fn":"\n(function() {\n  // 尝试找到并点击\"控件使用指南\"菜单\n  var allDivs = document.querySelectorAll('div');\n  for (var i = 0; i < allDivs.length; i++) {\n    var el = allDivs[i];\n    var text = (el.textContent || '').trim();\n    if (text === '控件使用指南') {\n      // 找到后触发点击\n      el.click();\n      return 'clicked: 控件使用指南';\n    }\n  }\n  return 'not found';\n})()\n","kind":"evaluate","targetId":"26A65F7EE9C46B98ACD58D0C72FF8AC2"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":457,"output":237,"cacheRead":56704,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57398,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774143095392}}
