{"type":"message","id":"182c6c89","parentId":"ed14a4d0","timestamp":"2026-03-22T01:33:38.269Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"页面可能需要登录才能查看具体的文档内容。让我检查一下页面是否显示需要登录的提示。\n\n不过，让我先尝试直接访问文档的API或者获取iframe中的内容。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a28239b07bea482ab6deef07","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","fn":"\n(function() {\n  // 检查是否有iframe\n  var iframes = document.querySelectorAll('iframe');\n  var iframeInfo = [];\n  for (var i = 0; i < iframes.length; i++) {\n    iframeInfo.push({\n      src: iframes[i].src,\n      id: iframes[i].id\n    });\n  }\n  \n  // 检查是否有登录提示\n  var loginPrompt = document.body.innerText.includes('请登录') || \n                    document.body.innerText.includes('登录后') ||\n                    document.body.innerText.includes('登录/注册');\n  \n  // 检查是否有具体的文档内容区域\n  var specificContent = document.querySelector('.markdown-body') ||\n                        document.querySelector('.article-body') ||\n                        document.querySelector('[class*=\"markdown\"]') ||\n                        document.querySelector('[class*=\"document\"]');\n  \n  return {\n    hasIframe: iframes.length > 0,\n    iframes: iframeInfo,\n    hasLoginPrompt: loginPrompt,\n    hasSpecificContent: specificContent !== null,\n    specificContentClass: specificContent ? specificContent.className : null\n  };\n})()\n","kind":"evaluate","targetId":"26A65F7EE9C46B98ACD58D0C72FF8AC2"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":646,"output":319,"cacheRead":62848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63813,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774143207917}}
