{"type":"message","id":"3da0b2bd","parentId":"7807cab5","timestamp":"2026-03-22T01:34:51.786Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"链接中没有直接的href。这意味着导航可能是通过JavaScript事件处理的，而不是通过链接。\n\n让我尝试另一种方法：查看Vue组件的数据，看看是否存储了文档的ID或URL。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_898aa2f2afb84f0f854f3770","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","fn":"\n(function() {\n  // 尝试获取Vue实例的数据\n  var app = document.querySelector('#app') || document.querySelector('[data-v-app]') || document.body;\n  var vueData = null;\n  \n  if (app.__vue__) {\n    vueData = 'found vue on app';\n  }\n  \n  // 尝试获取所有包含data属性的元素\n  var dataElements = document.querySelectorAll('[data-id], [data-key], [data-url], [data-href]');\n  var dataInfo = [];\n  for (var i = 0; i < dataElements.length; i++) {\n    var el = dataElements[i];\n    dataInfo.push({\n      text: (el.textContent || '').substring(0, 30),\n      dataId: el.getAttribute('data-id'),\n      dataKey: el.getAttribute('data-key'),\n      dataUrl: el.getAttribute('data-url'),\n      dataHref: el.getAttribute('data-href')\n    });\n  }\n  \n  // 尝试获取window对象中的数据\n  var windowData = {};\n  if (window.__INITIAL_STATE__) windowData.initialState = 'found';\n  if (window.__NUXT__) windowData.nuxt = 'found';\n  if (window.store) windowData.store = 'found';\n  \n  return {\n    vueData: vueData,\n    dataElements: dataInfo.slice(0, 10),\n    windowData: windowData\n  };\n})()\n","kind":"evaluate","targetId":"21FD65314090F090A53635A9941493F3"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":346,"output":382,"cacheRead":65280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66008,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774143279023}}
