{"type":"message","id":"7e0a522a","parentId":"cb1ba5b6","timestamp":"2026-03-22T01:35:24.949Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！我获取到了所有文档的信息！现在我有每个文档的entityId，可以用来构建文档的URL。\n\n从数据中，我可以看到文档URL的模式应该是：\n`https://vip.kingdee.com/knowledge/detail/{entityId}`\n\n让我提取我需要抓取的16个文档的entityId：\n\n通用字段：\n1. 文本字段 - entityId: 215128684791905280\n2. 整数字段 - entityId: 220142099956385536\n3. 小数字段 - entityId: 220153919438712064\n4. 日期字段 - entityId: 220180664904104960\n5. 复选框字段 - entityId: 221552451739577600\n6. 单选字段 - entityId: 612330514669526528\n7. 多选字段 - entityId: 612233444029691904\n8. 下拉列表字段 - entityId: 221555621978878208\n9. 附件字段 - entityId: 221558278130386688\n10. 图片字段 - entityId: 221557353186454784\n\n业务字段：\n1. 基础资料字段 - entityId: 221670300038589696\n2. 用户字段 - entityId: 254641688097079040\n3. 组织字段 - entityId: 254647978647448576\n4. 数量字段 - entityId: 254665469700247552\n5. 金额字段 - entityId: 254664210486415616\n6. 单据体 - entityId: 224093028694948608\n\n现在让我开始逐个访问这些文档并保存内容。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"太好了！我获取到了所有文档的entityId。现在开始逐个抓取文档内容。\n\n**进度汇报：已获取文档列表，开始抓取内容**\n\n第1个文档：文本字段"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1b876972ce254283a8dd12d0","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"open","url":"https://vip.kingdee.com/knowledge/detail/215128684791905280"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":7623,"output":499,"cacheRead":67072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75194,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774143309410}}
