{"type":"message","id":"8d8a0de6","parentId":"d8f93aea","timestamp":"2026-03-22T01:36:22.237Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我继续执行抓取金蝶云苍穹控件使用指南文档的任务。从之前的执行记录来看，我已经：\n\n1. 打开了页面\n2. 发现页面需要登录才能查看完整内容\n3. 从页面的NUXT数据中获取了所有文档的列表和entityId\n\n但是当我尝试直接访问文档详情页时，被重定向到首页，说明需要登录。\n\n让我尝试另一种方法：\n1. 回到专题页面\n2. 通过点击菜单项来导航到文档详情\n3. 从页面中提取内容\n\n或者我可以尝试：\n1. 查看是否有公开的API可以获取文档内容\n2. 查看页面源代码中是否包含文档内容\n\n让我先回到专题页面，尝试通过JavaScript直接获取文档内容。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我继续执行任务。让我尝试通过页面的API获取文档内容："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f1a98f00a0a2452bab37f94c","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","fn":"\n(function() {\n  // 尝试通过API获取文档内容\n  var entityId = '215128684791905280'; // 文本字段\n  \n  return new Promise(function(resolve) {\n    fetch('/api/knowledge/entity/' + entityId, {\n      method: 'GET',\n      credentials: 'include',\n      headers: {\n        'Content-Type': 'application/json'\n      }\n    })\n    .then(function(response) {\n      return response.json();\n    })\n    .then(function(data) {\n      resolve(JSON.stringify(data));\n    })\n    .catch(function(error) {\n      resolve('error: ' + error.message);\n    });\n  });\n})()\n","kind":"evaluate","targetId":"0BA8D99D11825A43C5C3670A80BD37D6"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":67530,"output":361,"cacheRead":8768,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76659,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774143369994}}
