{"type":"message","id":"87ac64a0","parentId":"bbc2434b","timestamp":"2026-03-22T01:36:32.138Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"API请求失败了。让我尝试其他方法。我可以：\n\n1. 尝试从页面的window对象中获取数据\n2. 或者尝试点击菜单项，然后获取内容\n\n让我先尝试从页面中找到文档内容的API端点。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a7017e71233c4a08a2352629","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","fn":"\n(function() {\n  // 检查window对象中是否有可用的数据\n  var windowKeys = [];\n  for (var key in window) {\n    if (key.toLowerCase().includes('data') || \n        key.toLowerCase().includes('state') ||\n        key.toLowerCase().includes('store') ||\n        key.toLowerCase().includes('nuxt') ||\n        key.toLowerCase().includes('vue') ||\n        key.toLowerCase().includes('api')) {\n      windowKeys.push(key);\n    }\n  }\n  \n  // 检查是否有axios或fetch拦截器\n  var hasAxios = typeof axios !== 'undefined';\n  var hasFetch = typeof fetch !== 'undefined';\n  \n  return {\n    windowKeys: windowKeys,\n    hasAxios: hasAxios,\n    hasFetch: hasFetch,\n    nuxtKeys: window.__NUXT__ ? Object.keys(window.__NUXT__) : []\n  };\n})()\n","kind":"evaluate","targetId":"0BA8D99D11825A43C5C3670A80BD37D6"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":465,"output":289,"cacheRead":76288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77042,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774143382572}}
