{"type":"message","id":"d8152cd0","parentId":"35794ad8","timestamp":"2026-03-22T01:37:04.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"API返回404。让我尝试从页面的网络请求中找到正确的API端点。我可以通过监控网络请求来找到正确的API。\n\n或者，我可以尝试直接点击菜单项，然后从页面上获取内容。让我尝试这种方法。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_94c70e4daa414250a2619f43","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","fn":"\n(function() {\n  // 尝试从页面HTML中找到API端点\n  var scripts = document.querySelectorAll('script');\n  var apiPatterns = [];\n  \n  for (var i = 0; i < scripts.length; i++) {\n    var content = scripts[i].textContent || scripts[i].innerHTML;\n    if (content.includes('/api/') && content.length < 10000) {\n      var matches = content.match(/\\/api\\/[a-zA-Z0-9\\/_-]+/g);\n      if (matches) {\n        apiPatterns = apiPatterns.concat(matches);\n      }\n    }\n  }\n  \n  // 查找页面中的数据属性\n  var dataElements = document.querySelectorAll('[data-api], [data-url], [data-src]');\n  var dataInfo = [];\n  for (var j = 0; j < dataElements.length; j++) {\n    dataInfo.push({\n      api: dataElements[j].getAttribute('data-api'),\n      url: dataElements[j].getAttribute('data-url'),\n      src: dataElements[j].getAttribute('data-src')\n    });\n  }\n  \n  return {\n    apiPatterns: apiPatterns.slice(0, 20),\n    dataInfo: dataInfo.slice(0, 10)\n  };\n})()\n","kind":"evaluate","targetId":"0BA8D99D11825A43C5C3670A80BD37D6"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":432,"output":358,"cacheRead":77760,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78550,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774143413650}}
