{"type":"message","id":"3ac4947c","parentId":"c5da1180","timestamp":"2026-03-22T01:38:11.253Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到的都是导航菜单的内容，而不是文档的具体内容。这说明页面可能没有加载文档详情内容，或者需要登录才能查看。\n\n让我尝试另一种方法：直接通过URL参数访问文档，并检查是否有内容加载。或者我可以尝试查看页面是否有iframe加载文档内容。\n\n让我先检查是否有iframe或其他嵌入内容。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f6b1660c7fd14a0099741c93","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","fn":"\n(function() {\n  // 检查页面是否有iframe\n  var iframes = document.querySelectorAll('iframe');\n  var iframeInfo = [];\n  for (var i = 0; i < iframes.length; i++) {\n    iframeInfo.push({\n      src: iframes[i].src,\n      id: iframes[i].id,\n      className: iframes[i].className\n    });\n  }\n  \n  // 检查页面URL和查询参数\n  var url = window.location.href;\n  var search = window.location.search;\n  var hash = window.location.hash;\n  \n  // 检查是否有路由变化\n  var nuxtRoute = window.$nuxt && window.$nuxt.$route ? {\n    path: window.$nuxt.$route.path,\n    query: window.$nuxt.$route.query,\n    params: window.$nuxt.$route.params\n  } : null;\n  \n  // 检查是否有弹窗或模态框\n  var modals = document.querySelectorAll('[role=\"dialog\"], .modal, .dialog, [class*=\"popup\"]');\n  var modalCount = modals.length;\n  \n  return {\n    iframes: iframeInfo,\n    currentUrl: url,\n    search: search,\n    hash: hash,\n    nuxtRoute: nuxtRoute,\n    modalCount: modalCount\n  };\n})()\n","kind":"evaluate","targetId":"0BA8D99D11825A43C5C3670A80BD37D6"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2153,"output":399,"cacheRead":80640,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83192,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774143477357}}
