{"type":"message","id":"29b9713d","parentId":"4189df77","timestamp":"2026-03-22T01:38:22.157Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"有5个modal（模态框），其中可能有一个是登录提示。让我检查这些模态框的内容。另外，我注意到URL没有变化，说明点击\"文本字段\"并没有导航到新页面，可能需要通过Vue Router来导航。\n\n让我尝试关闭模态框，然后查看页面内容。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4eba98fa8b2a4e4a8867b281","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","fn":"\n(function() {\n  // 关闭所有模态框\n  var closeButtons = document.querySelectorAll('.el-dialog__close, .close, [aria-label=\"Close\"], button.close');\n  for (var i = 0; i < closeButtons.length; i++) {\n    closeButtons[i].click();\n  }\n  \n  // 检查模态框内容\n  var modals = document.querySelectorAll('[role=\"dialog\"], .el-dialog, .modal');\n  var modalContents = [];\n  for (var j = 0; j < modals.length; j++) {\n    var modal = modals[j];\n    var style = window.getComputedStyle(modal);\n    if (style.display !== 'none' && style.visibility !== 'hidden') {\n      modalContents.push({\n        className: modal.className,\n        text: (modal.innerText || '').substring(0, 200),\n        display: style.display\n      });\n    }\n  }\n  \n  return {\n    closedCount: closeButtons.length,\n    visibleModals: modalContents\n  };\n})()\n","kind":"evaluate","targetId":"0BA8D99D11825A43C5C3670A80BD37D6"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":681,"output":331,"cacheRead":82752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83764,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774143491795}}
